are being hacked to death?

642
01:38:12,747 --> 01:38:16,635
Move! Kill that
slave and Sivagami!

643
01:38:17,952 --> 01:38:19,798
Kill Kattappa!

644
01:38:37,451 --> 01:38:41,503
