01:39:23,017 --> 01:39:24,382
Tell him, Sivagami!

653
01:39:43,838 --> 01:39:47,771
Both my sons have
a right to the throne.

654
01:39:48,363 --> 01:39:53,934
The one with more valour,
compassion and wisdom

655
01:39:54,048 --> 01:39:55,937
